WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.500
The chair is a galaxy deciding whether to become rain.

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:11.400
My hands split into clocks, birds, and unfinished equations.

00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:17.933
Neon fruit hums softly while the walls forget their names.

00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:24.767
Every mirror blooms at once, wearing all possible faces.

